{"tid":2078630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主派初選 52團隊搶灘  反送中 年輕勢力冒起","createTime":"2020-06-25T07:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T08:05:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92e2a5b2a7a64ebebd0d942edea3b0c1b9dc5548","tid":2078630,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:48:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200625/DOBALUNTJIJNSC5KEOKIWV56EA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2FDOBALUNTJIJNSC5KEOKIWV56EA%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=f78b4698\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2FDOBALUNTJIJNSC5KEOKIWV56EA%2F&h=ecc89a7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200625/DOBALUNTJIJNSC5KEOKIWV56EA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民主派初選 52團隊搶灘 <br />\n反送中 年輕勢力冒起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【立會選戰】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主派為9月立法會選舉舉行初選，初選提名期本月20日結束，昨正式公佈參加初選名單，合共於五大直選區、功能界別的「區議會（第二）」（超區）、衞生服務界收到52個團隊報名，當中除了傳統泛民政黨，還有一班在反送中後冒起的年輕人。有學者認為，大批年輕人參加初選反映年輕一代投入度高，相信可在初選讓部份政治新血突圍，至於最終能否奪35+則難以估計。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Dm9eJ0RxFMIQnabmE8UbAtxi5CE=/190x135/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PWG4M6SNZBRYSOFLOY7YLURLRY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDm9eJ0RxFMIQnabmE8UbAtxi5CE%3D%2F190x135%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPWG4M6SNZBRYSOFLOY7YLURLRY.gif&h=584380fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社民連梁國雄（左二）和岑子杰（左三）昨宣佈分別循新東和九西參與民主派初選，並獲工黨傾力支持。<br />\n<br />\n民主派初選下月11及12日投票，初選對各地區直選有不同目標議席，但初選部份地區產生的出戰名單，不但較上屆民主派取得席數多，甚至較今次爭取目標議席多。其中九龍東目標爭取三席，初選後會派五隊參戰；新東目標爭取六至七席，初選後會派七隊出選；新西目標及出戰名單均為六隊；港島及九西目標爭取四隊，但兩區出戰正式選舉名單有待初選有結果後再決定。<br />\n<br />\n今次參加初選民主派人士，<br />\n.............................................................<br />\n<br />\n民主動力召集人趙家賢表示，<br />\n..................................................<br />\n，同區另外一位參選人亦於審核程序期間以書面通知退選。<br />\n<br />\n該名獲酌情接納的報名人<br />\n.................................<br />\n及獨立的鄒家成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cfZ7e7WjxpEHJbBNXyym-sCyAjc=/1035x2740/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3LCU2BDXIKKLB33JM56TJ3QUCU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcfZ7e7WjxpEHJbBNXyym-sCyAjc%3D%2F1035x2740%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3LCU2BDXIKKLB33JM56TJ3QUCU.gif&h=d3da6cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學者：新一輩有機會入閘<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：衞生界四人角逐 岑敖暉攻超區<br />\n<br />\n社民連梁國雄和岑子杰昨宣佈分<br />\n.................................<br />\n去原有的自由，最佳應對方法「就係唔好理佢，做開嘅嘢照做。」<br />\n<br />\n港大民意研究所副行政總裁鍾劍華看過初選名單後，<br />\n.....................................<br />\n會大展拳腳是好事。他直言現在只是初選開始階段，社會氣氛是否熱烈是後話，加上未來仍有政府插手DQ等不確定性，能否達成35+目標仍是未知之數。"},{"pid":"739e2fce56dfe5c01f88919bcb02f7df5d1b3df2","tid":2078630,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:50:22.000Z","msg":"［行動po置頂］全民報哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2078606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2078606</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6d82735ed09e3e05b50c8a267601242f98a5fd5","tid":2078630,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:52:42.000Z","msg":"我烚㷬票 長毛不了"},{"pid":"5b12b2280c9de8b9fda00c2170b9f106c0a307f3","tid":2078630,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:57:22.000Z","msg":"6月27日(六) 開始 每晚 21:00 各區初選直播 《蘋果日報》、《立場新聞》、《D100》 及《城寨》合辦 政事<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2077854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2077854</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6月27日(六) 開始 每晚 21:00 各區初選直播 《蘋果日報》、《立場新聞》、《D100》 及《城寨》合辦 新聞<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2077862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2077862</a>"},{"pid":"37d1cc5bc991ad659fc744318c6f96d2ce0d41bf","tid":2078630,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:58:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5572d3bd7013a44e8ed1a6c897c1e054a089a82f","tid":2078630,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:03:42.000Z","msg":"越多人越好<br />\nDQ party"},{"pid":"14f20ad742f2215e4d7eaf8200a3ac60dbc738ac","tid":2078630,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}